\subtree{
\title{Notes}
\ul{
\li{OMERO uses group-based permissions (READ-ONLY, READ-ANNOTATE, READ-WRITE)}
\li{Images in OMERO are organized hierarchically: Project > Dataset > Image}
\li{Screening data uses: Screen > Plate > Well > WellSample > Image}
\li{Always close connections to free server resources}
\li{Use context managers for automatic resource management}
\li{Pixel data is returned as NumPy arrays for analysis}
}
}
}